<page section="release-3.7.1">
  <heading>Release 3.7.1</heading>

  <content>
    <para>
      <release-info version="3.7.1" />
      The 3.7.1 release fixes 2 minor issues.
    </para>

    <table class="release-notes">
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          DCS file-upload fix
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            DCS upload file function did not work after switching from GET to file-upload.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Bing errors
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Handle intermittent Bing errors better (by retrying).
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <hr />

    <p>
      For a complete list of improvements and bug fixes, see <a
      href="http://issues.carrot2.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?reset=true&amp;jqlQuery=project+%3D+CARROT+AND+fixVersion+%3D+%223.7.1%22+ORDER+BY+priority+DESC">JIRA
      issues fixed</a> in version 3.7.1. 
    </p>
  </content>
</page>

